{"tid":1369551,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"地盤工人致香港人","createTime":"2019-07-26T17:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T01:37:59.000Z","uid":290594,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"427b508048f651af47ba7cd0943c738c4c4b5a6a","tid":1369551,"uid":290594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:21:34.000Z","msg":"香港人：<br />\n我哋本身工作係手停口停，但因為睇到721元朗暴力事件同警黑合作問題，令到我地覺得不公義，而年青人走上街就因為極權政府、腐敗高官，用極權打壓各種有嘅自由，其次係政府可以用前線警察做盾自己就涼冷氣；所以我地明天罷工一起同年青人做同行者向不公義發聲，並要求回應以下訴求：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1.㯙回送中法<br />\n2.成立獨立調查委員會還良心警察清白<br />\n3.反對警黑合作<br />\n4.反對警察濫權問題<br />\n5.保護市民安全<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n                                                                         地盤佬上<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5QgmDgL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5QgmDgL.png&h=c5a1ba46&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1KMqku6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1KMqku6.png&h=054f2fc6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/doNMPos.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdoNMPos.png&h=484eddd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a91e032d692d4f44be7773f9a62a4b67d89c482c","tid":1369551,"uid":241297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:23:32.000Z","msg":"g持 推"},{"pid":"7f1ce3cdb1f2ba89d515136ef3abb8df6cbde227","tid":1369551,"uid":121131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:39:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c034fcecbba0917b4b402b2618ceb95fe9e306","tid":1369551,"uid":54253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:42:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f12883085352f3bac856983896cb39af59a7795","tid":1369551,"uid":43082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT